FeedPackage.Description:
GDS Google Map integrates an interactive Google Map into your desktop applications, providing a fast and convenient way for software developers to display customized geographic data on top of Google Map and perform Google Map based operations and computations.
It supports various map types: roadmap, satellite, hybrid and terrain and open street map.
It supports Google controls, map events and enables.
It supports various features and feature layers: DotPin, CharPin, IconPin, TextPin, Icon, Polyline, Polygon and Heatmap.
It supports various Google services: geocoding service, directions service, elevation service, geometry service and places service.
It supports autocomplete to find addresses or routes, traffic layer, transit layer, bicycling layer, street view and retrieving map image as bitmap.
FeedPackage.ReleaseNotes:
Minimal System Requirement: .Net 4.0 on Windows 7.
Please visit the project website to download the latest programming guide.
FeedPackage.Summary: GDS Google Map Desktop Control (WinForms or WPF) for .Net
FeedPackage.Tags: Google Map Control .Net C# WinForms WPF VB.Net
